{"tid":219343,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"俾錯signal個男同學搞到以為我鍾意佢 點算","createTime":"2017-04-27T07:02:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T13:20:50.000Z","uid":43557,"like":12,"dislike":176,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c129164dd505ebf2be664ce77b84bf6701fa207f","tid":219343,"uid":43557,"like":3,"dislike":23,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:02:29.000Z","msg":"我係班上都算受歡迎 可能生得白同長腿<br />\n咁今個sem上莊 成班都玩到好埋<br />\n有次出去飲酒 個個都飲到醉晒 including我<br />\n之後唔小心挨左落個男同學度 佢仲送我返屋企<br />\n過左兩日佢約我去ocean park 咁我見冇野做咪去囉<br />\n其實成程都玩得幾開心<br />\n點知佢臨走無啦啦捉住我隻手 同我表白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢：其實你知唔知我鍾意左你好耐 我都知你都對我有意思先會同我出黎<br />\n我：你誤會左喇 我對你冇意思（心諗緊點鬆開佢 佢好撚臭）<br />\n佢：點會呀 咁你今日又同我出黎？你又肯俾我請你入場同食飯？<br />\n我：咁呢d係男人要有既風度黎架ma 我難得同你出黎唔係仲要俾錢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後我講完之後9秒9沖左上bus冇理到佢 <br />\n而家仲震緊 乜d毒撚咁易鍾意人架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲d上基仲要成日對住佢 點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96bceec206ef6bb579b25874e196ff7c5f85aa69","tid":219343,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e946c247727d1a91225384cbb4d19a7f2d4090e4","tid":219343,"uid":20531,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:06:01.000Z","msg":"點解...明明你對我都有意思，咁樣欺騙自己有意思咩？"},{"pid":"8eb6242dd45534a31b44afaede9fad76f5dcadc5","tid":219343,"uid":105636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:06:30.000Z","msg":"係人都誤會喇"},{"pid":"a3181169d2c89ea474c179379f96edb358c0d343","tid":219343,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:06:48.000Z","msg":"閱."},{"pid":"b983053cecafa74447c1b4d9f0d07c72fcd73a97","tid":219343,"uid":48783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,