7-04-27T07:28:13.000Z","msg":"幾好笑"},{"pid":"dac2a9cca331bda73801ab45a203ed5385050717","tid":219343,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:29:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毒男實係對好易有好感啦<br />\n身邊冇女<br />\n但係你咁既signal係男人<br />\n都出事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飲酒果晚我都醉到唔知挨左落人地度<br />\n去op果日佢又冇問我拎返錢 <br />\n咁我覺得佢幾風度 我都廢事俾返錢佢<br />\n咁就出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f3dfc153b4e2ad376117e007ca6c006b9d9fb3","tid":219343,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:30:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ching ho ball</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d35537242aa42a898031402e5801d63f644e17","tid":219343,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:30:07.000Z","msg":"你係呀希？"},{"pid":"c5f2276e6276c9356fe89b649289be47fa6ecd27","tid":219343,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:30:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff0f912c92bc4b9eacb7e8f142a2e34ff55d5dcc","tid":219343,"uid":91916,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:30:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a1155b44b21174dcd33dfd163827ea672af969","tid":219343,"uid":108421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:33:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>毒男實係對好易有好感啦<br />\n身邊冇女<br />\n但係你咁既signal係男人<br />\n都出事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飲酒果晚我都醉到唔知挨左落人地度<br />\n去op果日佢又冇問我拎返錢 <br />\n<span style=\"col